name: RentalCarReservation
desc: A reservation to rent a car.

items.name: dropoffLocation
items.desc: The place where the renter returns the car.

items.name: dropoffTime
items.desc: The latest time the renter may return the car.

items.name: pickupLocation
items.desc: The place where the renter picks up the car.

items.name: pickupTime
items.desc: The earliest time the driver may pick up the car.

items.name: reservationFor
items.desc: The type of vehicle to be rented.

items.name: reservationId
items.desc: A unique identifier for the reservation, consistent in all markup.

items.name: url
items.desc: A webpage the user can access to view reservation details.
